---
title: Cheesy Baked Pasta and Meatballs with Spinach
description: Tonight's plate of pasta is a baked riff on spaghetti and meatballs. Penne tossed in tomato sauce and spinach is topped with meatballs before being layered with a generous helping of cheese and going under the broiler for a crispy finish!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/pates-et-boulettes-gratinees-49020cde.jpg
